---
const tableOfContents = [
  { title: "What is an Xbox Gamertag?", anchor: "what-is-gamertag" },
  { title: "Classic vs Modern", anchor: "classic-vs-modern" },
  { title: "How the Generator Works", anchor: "how-generator-works" },
  { title: "Tips for a Great Tag", anchor: "tips-great-tag" },
  { title: "Naming Rules", anchor: "naming-rules" },
  { title: "How to Claim Your Gamertag", anchor: "claim-gamertag" }
];
---

<section class="section-white-subtle py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Ad slot top -->
      <div class="bg-[#F3F4F6] rounded-xl px-4 md:px-6 py-6 text-center border-2 border-dashed border-[#D1D5DB] mb-8">
        <p class="font-ui text-sm md:text-base text-[#6B7280] mb-2">Advertisement</p>
        <div class="h-24 md:h-36 lg:h-40 bg-[#E5E7EB] rounded-lg"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Table of Contents -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[#E5E7EB] rounded-xl px-5 md:px-6 py-5 md:py-6 mb-10 shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(15,23,42,0.04)]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 pb-3 border-b border-[#E5E7EB]">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="0" y="1" width="14" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B" />
            <rect x="0" y="6" width="10" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B" />
            <rect x="0" y="11" width="12" height="2" rx="1" fill="#00D02B" />
          </svg>
          <span class="font-ui text-[12px] md:text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#00D02B]">
            Table of Contents
          </span>
        </div>

        <ol class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
          {tableOfContents.map((item, i) => (
            <li>
              <a
                href={`#${item.anchor}`}
                class="flex items-center gap-3 px-3.5 py-2.5 rounded-md text-base font-semibold text-[#374151] no-underline transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-[#00D02B]/[0.08] hover:text-[#00A021]"
              >
                <span class="text-[12px] font-bold text-[#00D02B]/70 min-w-[24px]">
                  {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
                </span>
                <span>{item.title}</span>
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- Article body -->
      <div class="prose-clean">

        <h2 id="what-is-gamertag" class="scroll-mt-24 article-h2">
          Types of Xbox Gamertags (The Gamertag Idea Factory)
        </h2>

        <p class="article-p">
          Now that you know how Xbox gamertags work—and how to create one that actually says something about you—it's time to explore your options.
        </p>
        <p class="article-p">
          We've built a massive, organized library of gamertag ideas designed to match every kind of gamer vibe.
        </p>
        <p class="article-p">
          Whether you're going for something funny, dark, aesthetic, or inspired by your favorite anime or game genre, this isn't just about throwing words together—it's about finding a name that fits your style, your energy, and how you show up in-game.
        </p>

        <div class="ad-slot my-8">
          <p class="ad-label">Advertisement</p>
          <div class="ad-box"></div>
        </div>

        <h3 id="classic-vs-modern" class="scroll-mt-24 article-h3">
          By Style &amp; Vibe
        </h3>

        <p class="article-p">
          Go by how you want your name to feel:
        </p>

        <ul class="article-list">
          <li><strong>Funny Xbox Gamertags:</strong> From harmless memes to chaotic energy.</li>
          <li><strong>Dark Humour Xbox Gamertags:</strong> For the edgelords among us.</li>
          <li><strong>Cool &amp; Stylish Xbox Gamertags:</strong> Sleek, bold, and battle-ready.</li>
          <li><strong>Aesthetic &amp; Soft Gamertags:</strong> Think cozy gamer-core meets Tumblr nostalgia.</li>
          <li><strong>OG &amp; Classic Style Gamertags:</strong> Clean, one-worders with legacy vibes.</li>
          <li><strong>Unique One-Word Gamertags:</strong> Minimal. Memorable. Marketable.</li>
          <li><strong>Pro Gaming Names:</strong> For when you're ready to compete—or fake it.</li>
          <li><strong>Gamertags for Streamers:</strong> Built with brandability and cross-platform swagger.</li>
          <li><strong>Multiplatform Gamertags:</strong> Great across Xbox, PS, Steam, and more.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="ad-slot my-8">
          <p class="ad-label">Advertisement</p>
          <div class="ad-box"></div>
        </div>

        <h3 id="how-generator-works" class="scroll-mt-24 article-h3">
          By Identity
        </h3>

        <p class="article-p">
          Match your tag to your voice and vibe:
        </p>

        <ul class="article-list">
          <li>Xbox Gamertags for Guys</li>
          <li>Xbox Gamertags for Girls</li>
          <li>Xbox Gamertags for Non-Binary or Gender-Neutral Individuals</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="ad-slot my-8">
          <p class="ad-label">Advertisement</p>
          <div class="ad-box"></div>
        </div>

        <h3 id="tips-great-tag" class="scroll-mt-24 article-h3">
          By Interest or Theme
        </h3>

        <p class="article-p">
          Dial in on what you love:
        </p>

        <ul class="article-list">
          <li><strong>Anime-Inspired Xbox Gamertags:</strong> From Naruto to Chainsaw Man fans.</li>
          <li><strong>Stoner &amp; Chill Xbox Gamertags:</strong> Laid-back, vibey, and probably listening to lo-fi.</li>
          <li><strong>Gamertags by Game Genre (FPS, RPG, etc.):</strong> Tailored to your playstyle.</li>
          <li><strong>Gamertags by Personality Trait:</strong> Based on you—not just what you play.</li>
          <li><strong>Gamertag Themes (Fantasy, Retro, Mythology etc.):</strong> Get creative with genre-inspired tags.</li>
          <li><strong>Xbox Gamertags for Sports Fans:</strong> Perfect for FIFA, 2K, and Madden junkies.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="article-p">
          No matter how niche or broad your taste is, there's a name set here to get the ideas flowing.
        </p>

        <div id="naming-rules" class="scroll-mt-24"></div>
        <div id="claim-gamertag" class="scroll-mt-24"></div>

        <div class="ad-slot mt-8">
          <p class="ad-label">Advertisement</p>
          <div class="ad-box"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>.prose-clean {
  color: #4B5563;
}

/* MAIN TITLE */
.article-h2 {
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.2vw, 2.6rem); /* bigger */
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: #111827;
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

/* SUB HEADINGS */
.article-h3 {
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw, 1.9rem); /* bigger */
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.3;
  color: #00B324;
  margin-top: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* PARAGRAPH TEXT (MOST IMPORTANT) */
.article-p {
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px; /* 🔥 increased */
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #4B5563;
  margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
}

/* LIST */
.article-list {
  list-style: disc;
  padding-left: 1.75rem;
  margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
}

.article-list li {
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px; /* 🔥 increased */
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #4B5563;
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}

.article-list li strong {
  color: #111827;
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* ADS */
.ad-slot {
  background: #F3F4F6;
  border: 2px dashed #D1D5DB;
  border-radius: 0.75rem;
  padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.ad-label {
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px; /* slightly bigger */
  color: #6B7280;
  margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
}

.ad-box {
  height: 7rem;
  background: #E5E7EB;
  border-radius: 0.5rem;
}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .article-p,
  .article-list li {
    font-size: 19px;
  }

  .ad-box {
    height: 9rem;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .article-p,
  .article-list li {
    font-size: 20px; /* 🔥 desktop readability */
  }

  .ad-box {
    height: 11rem;
  }
}
</style>